description:
Juan Martin Carrara and Stefania Colina dance “El puntazo” by Juan D'Arienzo at the 3rd Łódź Tango Salon Festival 2013 in Lodz, Poland.

There was a small blackout of the light in the middle of the song, they handled it like the pros they are!
